RGB VALUE

rgb(red,green,blue); 

HSL VALUE 

hsl(hue,saturation,lightness);
saturation - intensity of the color
lightness - how  much light u want to give the color


RGBA VALUE 

rgba(red,green,blue,alpha);

alpha - transparency - 0.0 => full transparent

